text: Byatki () is a rural locality (a village) in Kakrybashevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 146 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Tuymazy, 11 km from Kakrybashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Byatki
